onnomchea disa logn zal'le cholyen kullara yeupak zai, oso nem' asa. Tea disa ghorantlea nokrochakorank, dhoni novim lugttam bhettoitat. Bhattkaralim kullam tankam kellim,touxim, karande hea follancheo bhetti dhaddttat. Bhattkar godd-dhodd jeunn tankam vaddtta.

Molealom' bhaxent he porbecher don sundor kaveam rochleant tim oxim: vilvot'toyu raghoun nombiar hachem ‘ornnomula vilasom'’ ani perumpora vasudevo bhott'ttarthiri hanche ‘utt'ttritothi choritom'’. Keroll soddun tomillonaddu, kornattok vattharantuy onnom' porob adlea kallar zatali. Tomill allvarachim gitam, kornattokache doreadegelagosar gongaulli nhoinche lagim axil'lea ovxexamvelean hi gozal sidhd zata.


